    "TraditionalChinese": "穩定的二氫燃料"
  },
  "Description": {
    "English": "Highly reactive solid-state fuel, required to fuel <span class=\"name name-technology\">Starship Launch Thrusters</span>.<br><br>Created from crystallized <span class=\"name name-technology\">Di-hydrogen</span>, found in blue deposits on all worlds.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "高反应性固态燃料，用于为<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船发射推进器</span>充能。<br><br>可由晶体化的<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢</span>制成，这种晶体在所有世界的蓝色矿床中均可找到。",
    "TencentChinese": "高反应性固态燃料，用于为<span class=\"name name-technology\">飞船发射推进器</span>充能。<br><br>可由晶体化的<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢</span>制成，这种晶体在所有世界的蓝色矿床中均可找到。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "高活性固態燃料，有了它才能為<span class=\"name name-technology\">太空船啟動推進器</span>補充燃料。<br><br>以<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氫</span>晶體製成，所有世界的藍色資源產地皆能找到。"
  },
