  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "Craft Starship Launch Fuel from <span class=\"name name-technology\">Di-hydrogen</span> and <span class=\"name name-commodity\">Metal Plating</span><br><span class=\"name name-technology\">Di-hydrogen</span> is found in crystal form on most planets. Locate di-hydrogen crystals with the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Scanner</span> (<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>).<br>Metal Plating is crafted from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Ferrite Dust</span>. Use <span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span> to craft in empty <span class=\"name name-technology\">Inventory Slots</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢</span>和<span class=\"name name-commodity\">金属电镀</span>制作飞船发射燃料<br><span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢</span>在大多数行星上以晶体形式出现。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描仪</span>（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）定位二氢晶体。<br>金属电镀由<span class=\"name name-earth\">铁氧体粉末</span>制作而成。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">栏位</span>中制作。",
    "TencentChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢</span>和<span class=\"name name-commodity\">金属电镀</span>制作飞船发射燃料<br><span class=\"name name-technology\">二氢</span>在大多数行星上以晶体形式出现。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">扫描仪</span>（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）定位二氢晶体。<br>金属电镀由<span class=\"name name-earth\">铁氧体粉末</span>制作而成。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">栏位</span>中制作。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">二氫</span>和<span class=\"name name-commodity\">金屬電鍍</span>製作太空船啟動燃料<br><span class=\"name name-technology\">二氫</span>在大多數行星上以晶體形式出現。使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">掃描器</span>（<span class=\"name name-img\">SCAN</span>）定位二氫結晶。<br>金屬電鍍由<span class=\"name name-earth\">鐵氧體粉塵</span>製作而成。使用<span class=\"name name-img\">PRODMENU</span>在空置<span class=\"name name-technology\">欄位</span>中製作。"
  },
